-- Tennis Player Nalbandian Disqualified After Injuring Line Judge
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-06-17T15:01:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-17/tennis-player-nalbandian-disqualified-after-injuring-line-judge.html
     June 17 (Bloomberg) -  David Nalbandian  was disqualified
from the AEGON Championships tennis final against Marin Cilic at
Queen’s Club in London today after he kicked an advertising 
board into a line judge’s leg, injuring the official.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  